AWA by Dezygn - Marketing Brief

  One-Liner

  AWA is an AI creative director with a team of specialized agents working behind the scenes to deliver professional-grade design assets at scale.

  ---
  Hero Features

  1. Multi-Agent Intelligence

  AWA isn't just one AI—she orchestrates a team of specialized sub-agents:

  | Agent              | What It Does                                               |
  |--------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|
  | TaskRouter         | Understands your intent and routes to the right workflow   |
  | PromptEnhancer     | Transforms "make me a logo" into pro-level creative briefs |
  | ImageEditor        | Handles complex edits with 13 specialized techniques       |
  | VisionCritic       | Quality-checks every output before you see it              |
  | SearchOptimizer    | Researches difficult concepts via web search               |
  | ScreenshotAgent    | Captures & analyzes competitor websites for inspiration    |
  | ContentExtractor   | Pulls brand info from any URL                              |
  | BrandEvolver       | Learns and updates your brand identity in real-time        |
  | IngredientAnalyzer | Understands your uploaded assets automatically             |

  "It's like having a creative agency in your chat window."

  ---
  2. Batch Generation at Scale

  - Generate 100+ unique concepts in a single conversation
  - Each with its own creative direction—not just variations
  - Perfect for A/B testing, social campaigns, product lines
  - She'll show you the plan, get your approval, then execute

  ---
  3. Multi-Image Composition

  Upload multiple images and AWA intelligently combines them:
  - "Put my product on this background"
  - "Use photo A for the face, photo B for the pose"
  - "Combine these 3 product shots into one hero image"

  She shows you which source images she's using before generating—so you're always in control.

  ---
  4. Brand-Aware Everything

  - Learns your brand colors, fonts, personality, audience
  - Every generation is automatically on-brand
  - Can analyze competitor websites and extract their brand identity
  - Updates your brand profile through natural conversation

  ---
  5. Web-Connected Research

  Stuck on a tricky concept? AWA can:
  - Search the web for proven AI generation techniques
  - Screenshot and analyze any website for design inspiration
  - Extract product info from URLs
  - Find what works and apply it to your brief

  ---
  6. Transparent Reasoning

  - See her thinking process in real-time
  - She shows you the enhanced prompt before generating
  - Visual confirmation of source images being used
  - Quality verification on every output

  ---
  Differentiators

  | Traditional AI Tools          | AWA                               |
  |-------------------------------|-----------------------------------|
  | Single prompt → single output | Orchestrated multi-step workflows |
  | Generic results               | Brand-aware from day one          |
  | "Here's what I made"          | "Here's my plan—approve it first" |
  | One image at a time           | 100+ in a single session          |
  | Text-only input               | Images, URLs, screenshots, assets |
  | Black box                     | Transparent reasoning             |

  ---
  Use Cases to Highlight

  1. Social Media Manager: "Generate 30 unique Instagram posts for our product launch"
  2. E-commerce: "Put all 50 products on lifestyle backgrounds"
  3. Brand Manager: "Analyze 5 competitor sites and show me what makes them work"
  4. Creative Director: "Take these 3 photos and create a cohesive campaign hero"
  5. Startup Founder: "I have no brand yet—help me build one from scratch"

  ---
  Suggested Taglines

  - "Your AI creative team, not just a tool"
  - "From brief to 100 assets—in one conversation"
  - "The AI that shows its work"
  - "Brand-aware design at scale"
  - "9 specialized agents. 1 chat window. Unlimited creativity."

  ---
  Proof Points

  - 9 specialized sub-agents working in concert
  - 13 image editing techniques (removal, style transfer, composition, etc.)
  - 100+ images per session capability
  - Real-time brand learning that improves with every conversation
  - Web research built in—no tab-switching needed
  - Visual confirmation before every generation